Difference between jUnit and testNG?
A. Both TestNG and JUnit are open Sources. Both TestNG and JUnit are Testing frameworks used for Unit Testing.
TestNG is inspired by JUnit, so in a way these are similar. Few more functionalities are added to TestNG which makes it more powerful
than JUnit. Both JUnit and TestNG are without a doubt the most popular testing frameworks out there.

